sql:
SELECT date_time, maxtempC, mintempC
FROM weather_data
ORDER BY date_time DESC;

external_knowledge:
- 'warmest conditions': refers to the highest average maximum temperatures;
- 'last year': refers to the year 2023 in the context of this query;
- 'typical peak temperatures': refers to the average maximum temperatures over the year.

